    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "こころ、お疲れ様\n今日の収録、大盛り上がりだったな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kokoro‚ good work today.\nToday's recording was a huge hit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 6.5666667025
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "……え？　あぁ、ありがとうございます\nでも普段通りにしただけですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Eh? Oh‚ thank you.\nBut I just did what I usually do.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 14.1666667025
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうか……そうだ、スタッフさんから手土産にって\n話題のプリンシェイクをもらったんだ。飲んでみるか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I see… Right‚ the staff gave me this gift.\nIt's that famous pudding shake. Want to try some?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "へぇ、そうなんですね……後で飲んでみますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ I see… I'll drink it later.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.5666667025,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 27.7666673382
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "今日はなんか変だぞ。いつものこころなら\nプリンって聞いただけで真っ先に飛びつくじゃないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're acting strange today. Usually‚ if it's Kokoro‚\nyou'd jump at the mention of \"pudding\" instantly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.4000006358,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "というか最近ずっとそうだ。この間橋本さんが事務所に\nプリンを買ってきた時も、リアクションが薄かったし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually‚ you've been like this lately. Like when Hashimoto-san\nbrought pudding to the office‚ your reaction was weak.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.3490800876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 43.1333340049
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっとなんですかそれー。様子がおかしいかどうかの\n判断基準がプリンなのはおかしくないですかー！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wait‚ what's with that—! Is \"pudding\" really your only\nstandard for judging if I'm okay or not—!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.9528729061,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 50.8333322247
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "プリンを愛するこころだって\nたまにはプリンと距離を置きたい時だってあります！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even for Kokoro‚ who loves pudding‚\nthere are times when I want some distance from it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.7333321889,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 56.3333322247
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_01-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "さては最近こころに構ってもらえなくて寂しいんですね\nこころ不足ならそう言えばいいのに～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I bet you're just lonely because Kokoro hasn't played with you lately.\nIf you're suffering from \"Kokoro deficiency‚\" just say so~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.5333321889,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}